        "Box1image": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_244_5.png",
        "box1Heading": "Decrease Molting Times!",
        "box1content": "<p>GrubTerra dried black soldier fly larvae can help your chickens molt faster and stay healthy! Packed with protein and calcium, they give chickens the important nutrients they need for strong new feathers and a smooth molting season.</p>",
