        "box2Heading": "Speeds Up Feather Regrowth",
        "box2content": "<p>Molting requires extra protein to regrow feathers, which chickens often seek out while foraging. Black soldier fly larvae provide a concentrated protein source to help feathers grow back faster, even when free-ranging isn’t possible.</p><p></p>",
