        "box3Heading": "Sustainably Raised",
        "box3content": "<p>Grubterra’s Black Soldier Fly Larvae are raised on food waste, in farms located around the globe. Every 1 pound of grubs purchased diverts 20 pounds of waste from landfills.</p>",
