        "box4Heading": "Supports Immune Health When Chickens Are More Vulnerable",
        "box4content": "<p>Chickens are more susceptible to stress and illness during molting. Black soldier fly larvae support immune health with essential nutrients, giving them the boost they need to stay resilient through this taxing period without the added stress of free-ranging.</p>",
        "Box5image": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_244_9.png",
        "box5Heading": "Boosts Calcium for Feather Health and Eggshell Strength! 75X more calcium then mealworms!",
        "box5content": "<p>During molting, chickens need calcium for feather health and eggshell strength as they return to laying. Black soldier fly larvae deliver a natural source of calcium, supporting both healthy feather regrowth and strong eggshells.</p>"
